collections.name: Modular Manhua
collections.description: "Modular Manhua by Tianming" reconstructs the language of manhua—a Chinese tradition of illustrated storytelling—through the fractured lens of German Bauhaus and Cubist deconstruction. In Tianming’s latest series, faces are reduced to modular shapes, their identities shifting through intersecting planes of color, shadow, and form. Each of the 65 unique one-of-one NFTs breaks portraiture into its most essential components, where the act of seeing becomes a process of assembly and disassembly. Created using pastel and oil-based ink transfers on paper, these works were submitted to Orangehare.io and adapted as digital collectibles through in-house techniques.

collections.description:
Biryulyov Animals has been transporting animals around the country since 2020. On the way, we take care of animals, including medical manipulations of sick animals.

We mainly work with homeless animals from shelters, where often animals go to large cities for treatment or placement in new families. 

Biryulyov Animals NFT - it’s collection of photos about the transportation of animals around the country. Animals through the eyes of an animal carrier.

Part of the proceeds from the sale of Collection NFT Biryulyov Animals will be used to pay for the transportation of sick and homeless animals around the country to veterinarians or new families. 

Buy Collection Biryulyov Animals and help homeless and sick animals with me.

collections.name: Blue And Yellow Macaw
collections.description: The blue-and-yellow macaw (Ara ararauna), also known as the blue-and-gold macaw, is a large, vibrant parrot native to tropical forests, woodlands, and savannas of Central and South America, including Trinidad.  Blue-and-yellow macaws are intelligent, social birds that form lifelong bonds with mates and are excellent mimics of sounds, including human speech. Their diet includes fruits, seeds, nuts, and bark, and they use their strong beaks to crack open hard shells. They are popular in aviculture due to their beauty and trainability but face threats from habitat loss and the illegal pet trade despite being listed as Least Concern by the IUCN.

collections.name: MUSIC MEDICINE
collections.description:
"MUSIC MEDICINE - 音楽の処方箋"は、音楽家・酒本信太によるアート・プロジェクト。祈りと瞑想の音楽。

人間の意識の力を媒体に、愛と平和の未来の風景から、溢れ出る音楽が、人々のうちなる意識の変革にダイナミックに働きかけることを意図した。

AI時代において、過去に生成され音楽のデータの組み合わせで、無限に音楽を誰でも生成できる時代において、人間が奏る音楽の本当の意味とは何かを炙り出す、「人間の、人間のための、人間による音楽」。

‘MUSIC MEDICINE - Prescription for Music’ is an art project by musician Shinta Sakamoto. Music of prayer and meditation. Using the power of human consciousness as a medium, the music overflowing from the future landscape of love and peace is intended to dynamically work on the transformation of people's inner consciousness.

In the age of AI, when anyone can generate unlimited music by combining music data generated in the past, this is ‘music of humans, for humans, by humans’, which reveals the true meaning of music played by humans.

collections.name: Black Box
collections.description:
Scattered across time and space, hidden in the deepest trenches of the sea, buried beneath scorched earth, or sealed away in celestial vaults—the Forbidden Reliquary is a collection of the most enigmatic and terrifying artifacts ever known. Each box in this accursed archive is a vessel of untold power, containing horrors that defy comprehension.
Each of these relics holds a secret, a burden of knowledge too dangerous for mortal minds. To seek them is to invite madness. To open them… is to risk the end of all things.

🎨 THE POWER OF COLORS IN MY ART 🎨
This masterpiece is not just a simple composition of colors—it is a reflection of life itself. Every hue, every shade plays a crucial role in forming a harmonious whole, just as every human value contributes to the essence of our existence.
The way colors connect and complement each other represents the unity, balance, and warmth of human relationships, while the clashing, distant, or mismatched colors embody the chaos, conflicts, and disconnection in our world.
